metadata.name: Hoyo de Monterrey
metadata.description:
Tus manos firmes y seguras 
arrancan mis venas gruesas, 
cual virgen es desvirgada.  
Alisas mi áspera piel 
y la libras de impureza.  
Esas manos duras  
 me vuelven deseoso de orgías  
 entre madera, río y café.


Your firm and sure hands  
rip out my thick veins,  
which virgin is deflowered.  
You smooth my rough skin  
and free it from impurity.  
those hard hands  
 they make me want orgies  
 between wood, river and coffee.

attributes.value: Photograph sealed with original seal of recognized Cuban tobacco brand. The photo with a poem that reflect the story of severalwomen who dedicate their live  to the trade of tobacco cultivation
